<tr><td class="tableb"><h2><a href="#General_FAQ">General FAQ</a></h2><ul style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px"><li><a href="#How_Do_I_login">How Do I login?</a></li></ul><ul style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px"><li><a href="#Why_can_I_not_login">Why can I not login?</a></li></ul><ul style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px"><li><a href="#What_if_I_forgot_my_password">What if I forgot my password?</a></li></ul><ul style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px"><li><a href="#How_do_I_save_a_picture_to_&quot;My_Favorites&quot;">How do I save a picture to &quot;My Favorites&quot;?</a></li></ul><ul style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px"><li><a href="#How_do_I_rate_a_picture">How do I rate a picture?</a></li></ul><ul style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px"><li><a href="#How_do_I_post_a_comment_for_a_picture">How do I post a comment for a picture?</a></li></ul><ul style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px"><li><a href="#How_do_I_upload_a_picture">How do I upload a picture?</a></li></ul><ul style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px"><li><a href="#Where_do_I_upload_a_picture_to">Where do I upload a picture to?</a></li></ul><ul style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px"><li><a href="#What_type_and_size_of_a_picture_can_I_upload">What type and size of a picture can I upload?</a></li></ul><ul style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px"><li><a href="#What_is_&quot;My_Gallery&quot;">What is &quot;My Gallery&quot;?</a></li></ul><ul style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px"><li><a href="#How_do_I_create,rename_or_delete_an_album_in_&quot;My_Gallery&quot;">How do I create,rename or delete an album in &quot;My Gallery&quot;?</a></li></ul><ul style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px"><li><a href="#How_can_I_modify_and_restrict_users_from_viewing_my_albums">How can I modify and restrict users from viewing my albums?</a></li></ul><ul style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px"><li><a href="#How_can_I_view_other_users_galleries">How can I view other users galleries?</a></li></ul><ul style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px"><li><a href="#What_are_cookies">What are cookies?</a></li></ul><ul style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px"><li><a href="#Where_can_I_get_this_program_for_my_site">Where can I get this program for my site?</a></li></ul><h2><a href="#Navigating_the_Site">Navigating the Site</a></h2><ul style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px"><li><a href="#What's_&quot;Album_List&quot;">What's &quot;Album List&quot;?</a></li></ul><ul style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px"><li><a href="#What's_&quot;My_Gallery&quot;">What's &quot;My Gallery&quot;?</a></li></ul><ul style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px"><li><a href="#What's_the_difference_between_&quot;Admin_Mode&quot;_and_&quot;User_Mode&quot;">What's the difference between &quot;Admin Mode&quot; and &quot;User Mode&quot;?</a></li></ul><ul style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px"><li><a href="#What's_&quot;Upload_Picture&quot;">What's &quot;Upload Picture&quot;?</a></li></ul><ul style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px"><li><a href="#What's_&quot;Last_Uploads&quot;">What's &quot;Last Uploads&quot;?</a></li></ul><ul style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px"><li><a href="#What's_&quot;Last_Comments&quot;">What's &quot;Last Comments&quot;?</a></li></ul><ul style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px"><li><a href="#What's_&quot;Most_Viewed&quot;">What's &quot;Most Viewed&quot;?</a></li></ul><ul style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px"><li><a href="#What's_&quot;Top_Rated&quot;">What's &quot;Top Rated&quot;?</a></li></ul><ul style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px"><li><a href="#What's_&quot;My_Favorites&quot;">What's &quot;My Favorites&quot;?</a></li></ul></td></tr></table>
